{"tid":2501266,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"千人計劃｜中國出生科學家涉盜可口可樂技術 被裁定經濟間諜罪成","createTime":"2021-04-23T08:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T08:50:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0412810cffb8f16e3d9dc607e5f93d0578a83c","tid":2501266,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T08:50:40.000Z","msg":"在中國出生、其後移民美國的59歲華裔科學家游曉蓉（Xiaorong You，譯音）被指控在可口可樂等企業任職時利用職位之便，盜取涉及「不含致癌物雙酚A」（Bisphenol A Free，簡稱BPA-Free）技術的資料，再用作在中國成立新公司，且新公司獲中國政府「千人計劃」撥款。美國田納西州東區聯邦區域法院周四裁定她盜取貿易機密、從事經濟間諜活動等5項罪名成立，將在11月判刑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210423/KXKGNFJ2TVDZDGUMIX5YJ6QLNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210423%2FKXKGNFJ2TVDZDGUMIX5YJ6QLNU%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzluzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=67167006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210423%2FKXKGNFJ2TVDZDGUMIX5YJ6QLNU%2F&h=eb206c0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210423/KXKGNFJ2TVDZDGUMIX5YJ6QLNU/</a>"}]}